    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏里你将成为调查车祸案件的记者，帮助受害者并在必要时对其进行急救。获取事故证据并对案件进行推理，还原车祸发生的真实情况。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >检查受害者</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/f8db3bd915f63ddad3c9b45a33137f05.poster.avif?t=1769442307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/f8db3bd915f63ddad3c9b45a33137f05.webm?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/f8db3bd915f63ddad3c9b45a33137f05.mp4?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>首先评估受害者的伤势，然后对其进行急救！他们是否有呼吸？他们的身体是否出现严重的伤口？任何关乎他们生命特征的检查都会对他们的生存至关重要。对其进行急救、控制出血、检查脉搏，将其置于恢复体位。根据紧急情况的性质和严重性，对其采取一切必要的措施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作出决定</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/cf30eccf31f9eab9a32053d6bdc59071.poster.avif?t=1769442307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/cf30eccf31f9eab9a32053d6bdc59071.webm?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/cf30eccf31f9eab9a32053d6bdc59071.mp4?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>谁应该先得到紧急救援？最好的施救方案是什么？如果施救过程或者方案的选择出现错误，那么你不仅会使别人的生命处于危险之中，你自己的生命也将有可能陷入危险。三思而后行——时间不多了！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 时光倒流</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/27210dc6fe4a4952529a94e222ed5fd4.poster.avif?t=1769442307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/27210dc6fe4a4952529a94e222ed5fd4.webm?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/27210dc6fe4a4952529a94e222ed5fd4.mp4?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>你做了个错误的决定？没能救出所有受伤的受害者？你还是有机会解决这个问题的！启动时光倒流，再试一次。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找出事故背后的原因</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/1f43b79b6ca0ad873ac4f495a828a232.poster.avif?t=1769442307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/1f43b79b6ca0ad873ac4f495a828a232.webm?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/1f43b79b6ca0ad873ac4f495a828a232.mp4?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>当你在事故现场拯救他人的时候，每一秒都很重要，那时你无法对事故进行深入调查或找出事故背后的原因。但在救援任务结束后，你将要对整个事故进行详细分析，研究现场碎片，找出事故原因。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种不同的事故场景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/245fe85a409bc1a2a8237046adc432eb.poster.avif?t=1769442307\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/245fe85a409bc1a2a8237046adc432eb.webm?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/852220/extras/245fe85a409bc1a2a8237046adc432eb.mp4?t=1769442307\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>参与不同的救援任务：有简单的汽车碰撞，也有在不同时间，因复杂交通环境、天气状况而发生的严重连锁车祸。积累经验，学习如何在现实生活中帮助他人。</p>",
